  "description": "Just saw that Dwarf Fortress v 52.01 just came out, and the biggest part? \u0026ldquo;More powerful modding\u0026rdquo;\u0026hellip; that uses Lua. Which feels very affirming of my desire to create a Fennel game engine grounded in structuralism and similar thoughts. I don\u0026rsquo;t think folk know that\u0026rsquo;s what they want their sandbox to be made of, but they do, they clearly do: it\u0026rsquo;s what they made as a sandbox for their own cognition!\n",
